Document: VisibleOnScreenNotifier2D
Path: godot/classes/class_visibleonscreennotifier2d.rst
Summary: Overview of methods and signals for detecting screen visibility in 2D space.

Method: is_on_screen() → bool. const. Checks if the node is currently on the screen.

Signal: screen_entered(). Emitted when the VisibleOnScreenNotifier2D enters the screen.
Signal: screen_exited(). Emitted when the VisibleOnScreenNotifier2D exits the screen.
